00:00:12.530 --> 00:00:15.560
to do a talk on "Microtrends."

00:00:15.560 --> 00:00:16.730
Now, I'm up to "Squared."

00:00:16.730 --> 00:00:20.720
Hopefully 10 years from
now, "Microtrends Cubed."

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:23.750
Many of you will
