00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:35.150
at the world and figure out
how data drives me to trends,

00:00:35.150 --> 00:00:37.370
and what are some
of the implications,

00:00:37.370 --> 00:00:39.350
and how technology
and demographics

00:00:39.350 --> 00:00:42.290
are coming together to
create a lot of those trends.

00:00:42.290 --> 00:00:45.050
Now, 10 years earlier
I was just hugely

00:00:45.050 --> 00:00:48.380
