00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:54.500
of technology.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:57.680
But I think there's
more of a butt in it.

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:02.030
And I think I point out some
of my concerns and pitfalls

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:07.560
as technology goes to the
next level in people's lives.

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:11.090
Let me give you the theory
of the case of "Microtrends."

00:01:11.090 --> 00:01:12.830
What is a microtrend?

00:01:12.830 --> 00:01:15.680
Small, under the
radar trends that

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:19.490
could have enormous effects,
or that just give you

00:01:19.490 --> 00:01:23.300
kind of a shaped view of
society and how it's developing.

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:25.850
Think of the world
as a pointillist

00:01:25.850 --> 00:01:28.730
or as an impressionist
painting, and that you really

00:01:28.730 --> 00:01:30.500
kind of understand
some of the dots.

00:01:30.500 --> 00:01:32.660
And then there's
so many disruptions

00:01:32.660 --> 00:01:35.570
going on in society that
people don't understand.

00:01:35.570 --> 00:01:37.850
Part of the reason they
don't understand it

00:01:37.850 --> 00:01:40.250
is that underneath
the surface, there

00:01:40.250 --> 00:01:42.080
are trends and
counter trends going

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:46.100
exactly the opposite direction,
that society isn't really

00:01:46.100 --> 00:01:47.270
going in one direction.

00:01:47.270 --> 00:01:50.270
It's going in a multitude
of directions at once.

00:01:50.270 --> 00:01:52.550
And yet, together
they then represent

00:01:52.550 --> 00:01:54.740
a picture of what's happening.

00:01:54.740 --> 00:01:58.970
Look, elections were won or lost
on the basis of, say, 74,000

00:01:58.970 --> 00:02:01.990
votes, old economy voters.

00:02:01.990 --> 00:02:04.370
DACA recipients are less
than a million people.

00:02:04.370 --> 00:02:09.080
But they're a huge basis
of a political movement.

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:11.600
A bestselling book, it
doesn't really have to sell.

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:16.280
If I got up to 1%, I would
be an enormous author.

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:20.030
In fact, microtrends really
are critically important.

00:02:20.030 --> 00:02:23.860
And so I give you
50 in the book.

00:02:23.860 --> 00:02:26.990
I start with romance
and sex, because I

00:02:26.990 --> 00:02:30.510
