00:02:30.510 --> 00:02:34.790
But are there 500 or 5,000?

00:02:34.790 --> 00:02:35.900
There could be.

00:02:35.900 --> 00:02:37.670
I think you will
both get some insight

00:02:37.670 --> 00:02:38.780
into how I see the areas.

00:02:38.780 --> 00:02:40.910
I try to be generally
counter-intuitive.

00:02:40.910 --> 00:02:44.240
I try to do some things
