The medications, the radiation
has really serious consequences

00:17:38.840 --> 00:17:40.400
for millions and
millions of people.

00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:43.820
And then as soon as they drop
out of the emergency system,

00:17:43.820 --> 00:17:46.150
there's almost nothing in
terms of help or assistance.

00:17:46.150 --> 00:17:48.110
So part of
microtrends is finding

00:17:48.110 --> 00:17:51.770
