use some assistance,

00:17:51.770 --> 00:17:55.250
or brewing social problems.

00:17:55.250 --> 00:17:57.080
So kids on meds.

00:17:57.080 --> 00:17:59.870
I'm sure there are none here.

00:17:59.870 --> 00:18:05.090
But, in fact, 15% of America's
children, over 11 million kids,

00:18:05.090 --> 00:18:07.400
