00:18:07.400 --> 00:18:10.556
That's up from just
2 million in 1978.

00:18:10.556 --> 00:18:11.930
Now, there was
population growth.

00:18:11.930 --> 00:18:14.030
But it wouldn't
account for that.

00:18:14.030 --> 00:18:17.720
Now, remember at the
same time, health care

00:18:17.720 --> 00:18:20.360
became much more available,
and health insurance

00:18:20.360 --> 00:18:21.570
became much more available.

00:18:21.570 --> 00:18:26.920
So what was usually the province
of rich kids in private schools

00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:29.100
to have these kinds of meds
really could [INAUDIBLE]

00:18:29.100 --> 00:18:29.891
through the system.

00:18:29.891 --> 00:18:33.240
Now, is this a good
thing or a bad thing?

00:18:33.240 --> 00:18:35.000
We don't know.

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:38.490
It's mostly boys who wind
up with the diagnosis.

00:18:38.490 --> 00:18:41.390
And in order to
get through school,

00:18:41.390 --> 00:18:44.300
which requires an awful lot
of sitting still these days,

00:18:44.300 --> 00:18:48.110
these medications help a lot
of kids who might otherwise not

00:18:48.110 --> 00:18:48.920
be able to make it.

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:51.590
But do we know the long
term effects of this?

00:18:51.590 --> 00:18:54.710
Do we know whether it creates
another opioid type crisis?

00:18:54.710 --> 00:18:57.620
Do we know what to do with
the medications later on?

00:18:57.620 --> 00:19:01.220
80% of those with the
diagnosis get medication.

00:19:01.220 --> 00:19:04.670
This is an example of
something that's brewing,

00:19:04.670 --> 00:19:07.310
and that if we don't
give attention to it,

00:19:07.310 --> 00:19:10.430
we'll have a lot of social
problems that we didn't notice.

00:19:10.430 --> 00:19:14.090
And that's some of the
benefits of microtrends,

00:19:14.090 --> 00:19:16.390
and spotting them early.

