Apple, Google, I'm sure if
I read through the Google,

00:20:11.880 --> 00:20:15.780
it's very careful never to
call a collection of code

00:20:15.780 --> 00:20:17.910
a he or a she.

00:20:17.910 --> 00:20:20.850
Now, then I asked
Alexa the other day,

00:20:20.850 --> 00:20:22.920
