Alexa said, I am in
female character.

00:20:26.610 --> 00:20:28.500
What a slimy answer.

00:20:28.500 --> 00:20:29.930
OK.

00:20:29.930 --> 00:20:33.650
Alexa didn't admit
that Alexa is an it.

00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:36.500
It hid that fact from you.

00:20:36.500 --> 00:20:38.270
So I have a thing.

00:20:38.270 --> 00:20:41.620
Look, a lot of technology
starts out like this.

00:20:41.620 --> 00:20:44.120
There's a bot that
tells you the weather.

00:20:44.120 --> 00:20:46.120
It says, Mark,
it's going to rain.

00:20:46.120 --> 00:20:47.835
You might take your
raincoat with you,

00:20:47.835 --> 00:20:49.460
give a little more
time to get to work.

00:20:49.460 --> 00:20:50.100
Great.

00:20:50.100 --> 00:20:53.120
Thank you very much, bot.

00:20:53.120 --> 00:20:56.060
Now, back at headquarters
somebody says,

00:20:56.060 --> 00:20:58.397
we're helping out Mark and
like 50 million other people.

00:20:58.397 --> 00:20:59.480
And what do we get for it?

00:20:59.480 --> 00:21:00.720
Nothing.

00:21:00.720 --> 00:21:02.470
So somebody says, why
don't we make a deal

00:21:02.470 --> 00:21:03.890
with the umbrella company?

00:21:03.890 --> 00:21:04.750
They say, OK.

00:21:04.750 --> 00:21:05.317
Great.

00:21:05.317 --> 00:21:07.150
We'll make a deal with
the umbrella company.

00:21:07.150 --> 00:21:09.460
And now it says, hey,
Mark, it's going to rain.

00:21:09.460 --> 00:21:11.585
And, by the way, you can
get an umbrella right down

00:21:11.585 --> 00:21:12.610
at the corner.

00:21:12.610 --> 00:21:13.405
Perfect.

00:21:13.405 --> 00:21:14.524
Win-win.

00:21:14.524 --> 00:21:15.940
You now have a
good business model

00:21:15.940 --> 00:21:17.610
for telling me all this stuff.

00:21:17.610 --> 00:21:19.270
World is good.

00:21:19.270 --> 00:21:22.730
Now, somebody says,
earnings are coming.

00:21:22.730 --> 00:21:25.497
We're not really getting
enough money for Wall Street.

00:21:25.497 --> 00:21:26.080
What do we do?

00:21:26.080 --> 00:21:28.300
Somebody says, you
know that algorithm

00:21:28.300 --> 00:21:30.360
that says the weather,
it might rain.

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:32.710
Well, right now
we set it at 50%.

