Let's set it to 40%.

00:21:34.630 --> 00:21:37.290
Let's warn Mark when
it's 40% or 35%.

00:21:37.290 --> 00:21:39.460
Mark won't know the
difference, but he'll probably

00:21:39.460 --> 00:21:42.340
buy a few more umbrellas.

00:21:42.340 --> 00:21:44.830
Now, who is the bot working for?

00:21:44.830 --> 00:21:47.420
It started out working for me.

00:21:47.420 --> 00:21:51.020
Now, the bot is
primarily a salesperson.

00:21:51.020 --> 00:21:54.620
And I see a lot of technology,
agnostic to any company,

00:21:54.620 --> 00:21:56.520
