00:21:56.520 --> 00:21:59.990
And the problem is the
consumer has no idea.

00:21:59.990 --> 00:22:03.740
The consumer doesn't know that
there is a relationship here,

00:22:03.740 --> 00:22:05.600
and that it's changed
from being for me.

00:22:05.600 --> 00:22:07.100
And one of the
things in the book, I

00:22:07.100 --> 00:22:10.820
