disclosure about who

00:22:10.820 --> 00:22:14.570
or what is driving the
algorithms behind the bot.

00:22:14.570 --> 00:22:15.590
Is it working for me?

00:22:15.590 --> 00:22:18.980
Maybe I have to pay $20 a
month to get it to work for me.

00:22:18.980 --> 00:22:21.360
Or is it working
for advertisers?

