So if there's some
states that have

00:36:44.920 --> 00:36:47.980
some promising or good
initiatives for getting people

00:36:47.980 --> 00:36:49.840
off the couch by
changing their laws,

00:36:49.840 --> 00:36:53.770
or if maybe it's beyond just
the policy front, and just

00:36:53.770 --> 00:36:56.680
other ways that you can
get people off the couch

00:36:56.680 --> 00:36:58.030
