And I think actually that's
why I look at in this book,

00:49:28.980 --> 00:49:32.490
and I say protein is the big
trend I'd be looking at now.

00:49:32.490 --> 00:49:35.760
Vegan, 10 years ago I would have
been opening the vegan stands.

